<div className="col-md-12 mrgn-tp-0 mrgn-bttm-0">
<div id="2.3"></div>
<h3 id="sec-2.3">2.3 Other jurisdictions and federal departments</h3>  <p>The CNSC cooperates with other jurisdictions and federal departments to protect the environment. Where appropriate, the CNSC may enter into formal arrangements to increase the effectiveness of environmental protection. For example, the CNSC holds memoranda of understanding (MOUs) with other federal departments (for example, Fisheries and Oceans Canada, Environment Canada). A complete list of MOUs is available on the <a href="http://nuclearsafety.gc.ca/eng/acts-and-regulations/memorandums-of-understanding/index">CNSC&rsquo;s website.</a></p>
</div>
